Package game.specialSkill

Class SpecialSkill

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.actions.Action
game.specialSkill.SpecialSkill
Direct Known Subclasses:
QuickStep, Slam, SpinningAttack, Unseathe
public abstract class SpecialSkill extends Action
SpecialSkill class that extends Action to achieve DRY principle as it reduces codes of repetition This can be applied to some enemies and weapons as they can have a special skill!
